 I ia7 u7 chit8 e5 gau5 e5 jin5-sin5 mia5-kio3 Kiong Chi-ki5 kan3-cheng3 i kong2, Tek-khak m7-thang siu i chit nng7 hang7 le2-mih8. Na7 siu i e5 si5 tek-khak tioh8 lou7 chioh i ke3, iah8 au7-lai5 chin3 biat8 Kek-kok liau2-au7 chong2 bo5 tiaN7-tiaN7 ka7 lan2 chioh lou7 khi3 koan2 hia e5 peh-siN3; tek-khak lian5 lan2 e5 kok ia7 oe7 bo5--khi3. Lang5 kong2, Tun5-bong5 chhi2-han5 (chhui3-tun5 bo5--khi3, chhui3-khi2 chiu7 oe7 koaN5)chiu7-si7 chit e5 i3-su3. Sou2-i2 tek-khak m7-thang chun2 i e5 peng tui3 chia ke3. Chong2-si7 Gu5-kong e5 sim-koaN i2-keng hou7 hit e5 po2 be2 kap po2-gek8 be5 khi3, chiu7 in3 Kiong Chi-ki5 kong2, Chin3 kap Gu5 sng3 si7 siang7 ji7-siN3 e5 kok, i kaN2 put-jim2 lai5 biat8 goa2. Koh goa2 teh che3-su7 put-chi2 khian5-seng5, ia7 eng7 chin choe7 ho2 mih8 an2-ni sin5-beng5 tek-khak oe7 po2-pi3 goa2. Kiong Chi-ki5 kong2, Che long2 boe7 kho3 tit e5 su7, Chin3 oe7 hiah toa7 kok ia7 si7 u7 thun-chiam3 chong-chok8 lai7 kui2-na7 kok, koh hian7-si5 beh khi3 biat8 i e5 Kek-kok, kiam2 m7 si7 iu5-goan5 siang7 chong-chok8? Iah8 hit e5 sin5-beng5 e5 su7 sng3-si7 bong5-bong5 biau2-biau2, bo5 iaN2 bo5 chiah; siat-su2 Chin3 na7 chiong Gu5-kok biat8 khi3 liau2, ia7 iu5-goan5 eng7 ho2 mih8 lai5 che3-hian3, hit e5 sin5-beng5 kiam2 u7 kong2 oe7 thou3 chhut lai5 heng5 i mah? Sou2-i2 che long2 si7 boe7 kho3 tit e5 su7. Kiong Chi-ki5 an2-ni u7 chhui3 kong2 kau3 bo5 noa7, m7-ku2 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang i-ti7 Gu5-kong e5 tham-sim. Sou2-i2 Gu5-kong m7 thiaN i khou2-khng3; keng3-jian5 tui3 Chin3-kok e5 su3-chia2 tah-eng3 lou7 beh chioh i ke3. 
 Kiong Chi-ki5 chiu7 to3-khi3, kau3 in chhu3 e5 si5 chiu7 tui3 lang5 kong2, Lan2 e5 jin5-kun kong2 kio3 sin5-beng5 oe7 po2-pi3 i, goa2 khoaN3 chiah-e5 sin5-beng5 kin-ni5 e5 ji7-kau2-mi5 bo5 thang koh-chai3 chiah8 tioh8 Gu5-kok e5 che3-mih8. Kong2-liau2 chiu7 chiong i e5 bou2-kiaN2 ia7 soa3 poaN chhut kok-goa7, chau2 khi3 tiam3 ti7 Cho5-kok. Ko2-jian5 ti7 hit ni5 e5 ni5-be2, Chin3 e5 peng khi3 biat8 Kek-kok liau2-au7 khai2-soan5 beh to3-lai5 e5 si5, iu5-goan5 tui3 Gu5-kok keng-ke3, chiu7 sun7-soa3 chiong Gu5-kok ka7 I biat8 khi3, soa3 liah8 Gu5-kong kap in e5 tai7-hu-koaN Pek-li2 He5 to3-khi3 in kok-nih8. 
 Lang5 kong2, Chai thang kau3-giah8 chiu7 boe7 siu7 leng5-jiok8, chai thang hioh-khun3 chiu7 boe7 u7 gui5-hiam2. Che si7 teh keng2-kai3 lang5 tioh8 an-hun7 siu2-ki2, m7-thang sim-koaN siuN toa7 e5. Chong2-si7 kong2 khiok si7 khah khoai3; na7-si7 beh chiau3 an2-ni lai5 kiaN5 si7 chin oh. In-ui7 chit8 tiam2 tham e5 sim-koaN chin oh-tit tu5 khi3. Tui3 kou2-cha2 kau3 taN u7-e5 biat8 kok, u7-e5 kheng ka, u7-e5 pai7-hoai7 mia5-siaN, u7-e5 sit-loh8 siN3-mia7, choe7-choe7 si7 tui3 chit ji7 lai5. U7-e5 khah li7-hai7 e5 piN3 kau3 hong5-te3 choe3 ke3 chhiu2, siN3-mia7 chiah bo5--khi3. U7-e5 be7-cheng7-be7 su7 chiu7 phoa3, hou7 koaN--lang5 liah8-khi3 teng7 si2-heng5; bo5 m7 si7 ui7-tioh8 tham lai5 khi2-kian3. Sou2-i2 tui3 soe3-han3 e5 si5 eng-kai tioh8 seng tui3 chit hang7 e5 siu-sin lai5 ti3-i3. Chiu7-si7 tak8 lang5 bo5 m7 tioh8 eng7 teng2-bin7 hit nng7 cham7 e5 kou3-su7 lai5 choe3 keng2-kai3. Siok8-gu2 u7 kong2, Tham--ji7 pin5--ji7 khak, sou2-i2 lang5 na7 oe7 chai-chiok chiu7 sim-koaN ho5 si5 m7 peng5-an. Seng3-keng ia7 u7 kong2, Tham-chai5 si7 choe3 ban7 hang7 phaiN2 e5 kun-goan5. Ki5-sit8 bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 su7 na7 u7 chit8 ji7 tham--ji7 ti7 sim-lai7, chiu7 long2 kau3-giah8 thang hai7 lang5. 
 Oe7 siu2 chiah si7 Gau5 
 Tio7 Siong-chu2 khi3 kong-phah Tek8-kok u7 tek-seng3. Tek8-kok u7 nng7 e5 siaN5 kio3-choe3 Tiong-jin5 Lo2-jin5. Teh kou3 hit nng7 e5 siaN5 e5 koaN-hu2 u7 chhe su3-chia2 lai5 beh kiN3 Siong-chu2, kam-goan7 chiong in e5 siaN5-ti5 lai5 kui-hang5; hit-si5 Siong-chu2 tu2-a2 teh chiah8 e7-tau3 thiaN-liau2 ia7 bo5 sim2-mih8 hoaN-hi2 e5 khoan2. I e5 kun-lang5 khoaN3-liau2 chin ki5-koai3; chiu7 mng7 i kong2, Chit8 jit8 e5 tiong-kan, tit-tioh8 nng7 cho7 e5 siaN5-ti5, iu7-koh bo5 sim2-mih8 toa7 chhut-lat8, a2-si7 liau2 siuN choe7 pun2, an2-ni sng3 si7 chit8 kiaN7 thang hoaN-hi2 e5 tai7-chi3, chaiN2-iuN7 chu2-kong e5 bin7 hoan2-tng2 u7 iu-chhiu5 e5 khoan2, che hou7 goan2 chin boe7 hiau2-tit. Siong-chu2 chiu7 in3 i kong2, Hit-ho7 kang-ho5 e5 toa7 lau5-chui2, put-ko3 saN nng7 jit8 chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 the3 khi3; hit ho7 he7-thiN e5 toa7 hong-hou7 kek8-ku2 chit8 poaN3 jit8 ia7 chiu7 peng5-cheng7. Hian7-chai7 lan2 Tio7-kok bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 toa7 tek-heng7, chit8 jit8 tit-tioh8 nng7 cho7 e5 siaN5-ti5, i2-keng sng3 choe3 si7 kiaN5 kau3 kek8 koaiN5 e5 sou2-chai7; kiaN oe7 tui3 an2-ni liau2-au7 chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 soe-pai7 khi3 lah. 
 Hit si5 Khong2-chu2 thiaN-kiN3 chit e5 tai7-chi3 chiu7 kong2, Tio7-kok si7 teh beh heng e5 tiau7-thau5; tui3 kou2-cha2 i2-lai5 hoan5-lo2 iu-chhiu5 si7 oe7 hou7 lang5 heng-ong7; hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 si7 oe7 hou7 lang5 pai7-bong5. Oe7 tek-seng3 boe7 kong2-tit si7 oh e5 su7, tioh8 oe7 po2-siu2-tit kau3 kiu2-oan2, he chiah si7 ui5-lan5 e5 tai7-chi3. 
 Kou2 lang5 gian5 kong2, Hian7-si5 e5 se3-kai3, m7-tan7-na7 chhong3 su7-giap8 ui5-lan5, beh lai5 oe7 po2-siu2-tit ia7 m7 si7 iong5-iN7 e5 su7, sit8-chai7 chin u7-iaN2. Chong2-si7 lang5 na7 ti7 khoai3-lok8 e5 si5 m7-thang boe7 ki3-tit kan-khou2 hit-tiap8, ia7 m7-thang chiah8 pa2 boe7 ki3-tit iau si5. An2-ni chiah lioh8-a2 oe7 po2-tit i chit8-si3 lang5 boe7 siuN li7-keng; na7 bo5 chiu7 nng7-lin3-poaN3 iu7-koh peng2-loh8 lai5. Chong2-si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 lai7 e5 lang5 ia7 tioh8 ai3 chin soe3-ji7. U7 chit8 khoan2 e5 hoe7-iu2 chit8-e7 jip8-kau3, iah8 chiu7 hia-hia pai-pai ka-ki7 chin tek-i3, na2-chhin-chhiuN7 thian-kok e5 so2-si5 i2-keng ti7 i chhiu2 tiong-ng-nih8, hit e5 thian-kok e5 bian2-liu5 i2-keng ti7 i hau-pau-a2 lai7. Long2 bo5 siuN7 kau3 Seng3-keng-nih8 ia7 u7 beng5-beng5 kong2-ke3. KiN3-na7 chheng-hou goa2, Chu2 ah, Chu2 ah hit ho7 e5 lang5 bi7 pit-jian5 long2 oe7 chin3-jip8 thian-kok. An2-ni thang chai chit ho7 jip8-kau3 e5 su7, sui-jian5 si7 chin iau3-kin2, chong2-si7 hit ho7 chin-chiaN3 kau3-iu2 e5 tek-heng7, si7 keng3 koh khah tioh8 iau3-kin2. 
 Chit8 lang5 chit8 hang7 tioh8 
 Chai7-cha2 ti7 Chi-na2 SoaN-tang Che5 Lou2 nng7 kok e5 kau-kai3, hit sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 siN saN e5 kiaN2; in lau7-pe7 chiu7 the3 i chhe7 chhut-mia5 e5 sian-siN lai5 ka3-si7 i jin5-gi7 e5 to7-li2. Au7-lai5 kau3 chut-giap8 to3-lai5, in lau7-pe7 mng7 in kong2, Jin5-gi7 e5 to7-li2 chaiN2-iuN7 kong2? Hit e5 toa7 kiaN2 chiu7 in3 kong2, Jin5-gi7 si7 kio3 goa2 tioh8 thiaN3-sioh seng-khu, jian5-au7 choe3-chiaN5 ho2 e5 mia5-siaN. Hit e5 te7 ji7 kiaN2 kong2, Jin5-gi7 si7 kio3 goa2 tioh8 pang3-sak seng-khu, lai5 chiaN5 jin5-ai3 e5 mia5-siaN. Hit e5 te7 saN kiaN2 kong2, Jin5-gi7 si7 kio3 goa2 tioh8 po2-hou7 seng-khu, chiau3-kou3 mia5-siaN, nng7 hang7 long2 oe7 chiau5-chng5. TaN in chit saN e5 hiaN-ti7-a2 siang7 si7 chit8 e5 sian-siN ka3-si7 in, m7-ku2 in tai7-ke e5 kian3-kai2 long2 si7 toa7-toa7 bo5 saN-tang5. 
 Ti7 In3-tou7 e5 sou2-chai7 bat u7 lang5 khan chit8 chiah chhiuN7 tui3 koe-chhi7-nih8 ke3,u7 lang5 kong2 hit chiah chhiuN7 si7 ou-e5, u7 lang5 kong2 hit chiah chhiuN7 si7 peh8-e5, u7 lang5 kong2 hit chiah chhiuN7 si7 hoe-sek e5; tai7-ke chiN3 kau3 khia7 chin khia7 hian7, long2 m7 kheng2 sio-niu7, tit8-tit8 beh oan-ke khi2 lai5. Au7-lai5 lang5 chiah khi3 chha5 khoaN3 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 sek, chiah chai saN lang5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 long2 u7 chit8 hang7 tioh8. In-ui7 hit chiah chhiuN7 chit8 peng5 si7 ou-e5, chit8 peng5 si7 peh8-e5. Ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 kan-ta khoaN3-kiN3 peh8-sek, sou2-i2 kong2 si7 peh8 chhiuN7; ti7 to3-peng5 e5 kan-ka khoaN3-kiN3 ou sek, sou2-i2 kong2 si7 ou chhiuN7. Ia7 hit e5 ti7 thau5-cheng5 e5 khoaN3-kiN3 ia7 u7 peh8 ia7 u7 ou, sou2-i2 kong2 si7 hoe-sek e5 chhiuN7. 
 Koh u7 chit8 hang7 chhin-chhiuN7 hoa3-seng e5 lui7. U7 chit8 khoan2 thang5, chham kim-ku beh saN-siang7 khoan2, chong2-si7 i e5 sek-ti7 chit8 jit8 piN3 kui2-na7 sek. Bat ti7 cha2-khi2 si5 liah8 lai5 ka7 i khoaN3 si7 kim e5 sek-ti7; kau3 e7-pou ka7 i khoaN3 piN3 choe3 chhiN-e5; bin5-a2-cha2 khi2 iu7 piN3 choe3 ou-e5, a2-si7 piN3 choe3 hoe-sek e5, long2 bo5 tiaN7-tioh8. Si7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 teh chhi7 chham5-a2 (niu5-a2); cha2-khi2 khoaN3 si7 thang5, e7-pou khoaN3 chit8 liap8 phok8-a2(chham5-kian2); bin5-a2-chai3 ka7 theh8 chhut lai5 khoaN3-liau2 chit8 liap8 chhin-chhiuN7 thou5-tau7-jin5; keh chit8 poaN3 jit8 iu7 piN3 chiah be2-iah8 chhut-lai5; iah8 chiu7 oe7 kang-bu2 saN thin7, koh pang3 nng7 lai5 piN3-choe3 chham5-a2. Chong2-si7 na7 he long2 m7-bat khoaN3-kiN3 e5 lang5, thiaN-lian2 chiu7 chin giau5-gi5. 
 Ia7 koh chit8 khoan2 kou3-chip put-hok8-jin5 e5, chhin-chhiuN7 khoaN3-kiN3 chhiuN7 e5 chit8 peng5, chiu7 liah8 choe3 i bak8-chiu sou2 khoaN3 si7 an2-ni, chiu7 ngi7-ngi7 liah8 choe3 an2-ni tioh8. Chong2-si7 na7 chhin bak8 khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni chiN3 iau2 oe7 kong2-tit. U7 chit8 cheng2 hiah-e5 be5-sin3 kui2-sin5 e5 su7, beng5-beng5 to bo5 iaN2 e5 tai7-chi3 ia7 saN-kap hu7 hoe7-chong7 kau3 chin tu2 chin, hian7 tu2 hian7, boh8-kioh bak8-chiu u7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 su7, chu7-jian5 tek-khak si7 beh chiN3 kau3 iaN5. An2-ni kho2-kian3 se3-kan su7 si7 chin khoah, m7-thang eng7 ka-ki7 sio2-khoa2 e5 ti3-sek, chiu7 beh ka7 i toan3 kong2 si7 chaiN2-iuN7; long2 tioh8 khoaN3 hit e5 su7-the2 u7 hap8 to7-li2 than3 hoat-tou7 a2 bo5, chiah thang khi3 kiaN5. 
 Oe7 chiu7 bo5 Ui5-lan5 
 Hok8 Chu2-chian7 teh choe3 Sian7-hu2 e5 toe7-hng koaN, hit si5 Iu2-jiok8 khi3 chhe7 i; khoaN3-kiN3 i piN3 chin siau-san2, chiu7 mng7 i si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3. Hok8 Chu2-chian7 in3 i kong2, Li2 long2 m7 chai mah? Goa2 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5, phai3 goa2 lai5 choe3 Sian7-hu2 e5 toe7-hng koaN; in-ui7 tai7-chi3 chin choe7, put-chi2 bo5 eng5, sim-lai7 ia7 chin hoan5-lo2, sou2-i2 seng-khu chiah oe7 chiah-nih8 siau-san2 lah. Iu2-jiok8 kong2, Kou2-cha2 e5 si5, Sun3 teh choe3 hong5-te3, i toaN5 ngou2-hian5 e5 khim5, chhiuN3 lam5-hong e5 si, choe3 i an-han5 chu7-chai7, thong kok iu5-goan5 si7 liau7-li2 kau3 ho2-se3 ho2-se3. Hian7-chai7 chit e5 sio2-sio2 khoa2-khoa2 e5 Sian7-hu2 na7-tiaN7, li2 chiu7 hoan5-lo2 kau3 long2 boe7 hiau2-tit thang ti7-li2; siat-su2 hou7 li2 choe3 hong5-te3 lai5 koan2 kui kok, iah8 beh an2-chaiN2-iuN7 leh? 
 Lan2 lang5 ti7 chit se3-kan, tioh8 u7 hit-hang7 e5 pun2-su7, chiah oe7 pan7 tit hit-hang7 e5 su7-giap8. Siat-su2 to bo5 hit ho7 toa7 chai5-tiau7, kan-ta siuN7 beh choe3 hit ho7 toa7 su7-giap8, tek-khak si7 chiong hiah-e5 tioh8-boa5 kui ti7 khang-khang. Siok8-gu2 kong2, Ti3 chioh8 cheng-khu7 teh thiau3 ka-koan; chhut chin choe7 lat8 koh m7 ho2 khoaN3, chiu7-si7 chit e5 i3-su3. Chong2-si7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2, Hok8 Chu2-chian7 choe3 Sian7-hu2 e5 toe7-hng koaN, sui-jian5 si7 bo5 toa7 chai5-tiau7, khiok ia7 chin7 sim lai5 liau7-li2; sou2-i2 boa5 kau3 ka-ki7 e5 sin-the2 long2 siau-san2 khi3. M7-ku2 Sian7-hu2 e5 kau3-hoa3 toa7 heng-khi2, an2-ni sng3 si7 toa7 ho2 e5 koaN-oan5. Na7 pi2-pheng7 iau2 chit8 khoan2, chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 chai5-tiau7 iu7 bo5, chi3-khi3 iu7 toa7, kan-ta kou3 i ka-ki7 oe7 pui5, m7 koan2 peh-siN3 chaiN2-iuN7 kan-khou2, che chiu7 thian chha ti7 ian lah. 
